          "description": "Here\u2019s a 5-star review for a doctor\u2019s clinic:\n\n\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\nThe staff was incredibly welcoming and attentive from the moment I walked in. The waiting area was clean and comfortable, and my wait time was minimal. Dr. Rashan  was exceptional patient, thorough, and genuinely listened to all my concerns. They took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure I felt comfortable with the treatment plan. The follow-up process was smooth, and I felt supported every step of the way. Highly recommend this clinic to anyone seeking compassionate and professional care",
