          "description": "About two weeks ago I scheduled an appointment. I been to this location before and I can say that I agree with some of the other reviews about the staff being unprofessional. I like the Gynecologist that I was assigned and that\u2019s the only reason why I returned. However, this time I show up to my appointment and they notify me that my insurance is no longer accepted. I got reminder calls and emails about this appointment which is great but I guess no one had the efficiency to notify me that my insurance was no longer  accepted. Then the lady at the front desk had the audacity to tell me \u201c it\u2019s right there in the poster\u201d as if is my fault for this issue. If you consider this location, just make sure that you triple check so they don\u2019t waste your time.",
